	<section_number>18.2-7</section_number>
	<catch_line>Criminal act not to merge civil remedy</catch_line>
	<text>
		The commission of a crime shall not stay or merge any civil remedy.
	</text>
	<history>Code 1950, § 18.1-7; 1960, c. 358; 1975, cc. 14, 15.</history>
</law>
